# 🎨 Color Psychology & Visual Design System  
## Digital Talent Management Platform – UX Case Study

---

## 📌 Overview

In this platform, color is treated as a **functional UX system**, not just a visual layer.

It is used to:

- Reduce cognitive load  
- Communicate system states instantly  
- Guide user attention  
- Reflect emotional states across journeys  

A structured **semantic color system + neutral foundation + hierarchy rule (60-30-10)** ensures consistency and usability.

