# 🎯 4. Color Strategy: 60-30-10 Rule

To maintain visual balance and avoid clutter, the interface follows the **60-30-10 rule**.

---

### 📊 Distribution

- **60% Dominant (Neutral)**  
  - White / Light Grey background  
- **30% Secondary (Brand Color)**  
  - Blue (navigation, layout structure)  
- **10% Accent (Semantic Colors)**  
  - Green, Red, Yellow for actions  

---

### 🧠 Why This Works

- Creates **visual hierarchy**  
- Reduces cognitive load  
- Prevents color overload  
- Improves scanning efficiency  

